><p data-block-id=\"3d009435-05e1-4dd0-8e3d-8c38c7e5ca76\">Push Notification</p><p data-block-id=\"3defe89e-0791-4760-80ef-6058d12d4775\">&lt;put your video and screenshot&gt;</p></li></ul><h2 data-block-id=\"7cacbff0-6097-4577-8bea-2670eefceb05\"></h2><p data-block-id=\"3a86b5ec-38da-4400-83d2-ef1024cbe6c9\"></p><p data-block-id=\"12295416-ce37-4b1f-ae9c-e422707d5254\"></p><p data-block-id=\"8e9aac87-b7ff-4f0e-b9c9-0178d8f76e42\"></p><p data-block-id=\"1fba7422-3f0f-475f-a3cd-ed72e33bce4f\"></p><p data-block-id=\"acd97665-43b1-498b-89ca-e66b24c0a68f\"></p><p data-block-id=\"490a489a-2a58-4dc9-96ea-9e5cc09fc8be\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Maybank Online Banking","Description":null},{"Code":"id","Title":"Maybank Online Banking","Slug":"maybank-online-banking","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"18f0e858-8ed1-4280-93a0-fb7d06084bb3\"><img data-block-id=\"1a57d552-d3a8-4cc4-96d0-f4c9ea817e65\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/images (2).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"217\" height=\"60\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:217px;height:60px;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"9972d4bc-3cee-4a8f-b2ad-e655435ef5e6\">Maybank, salah satu lembaga keuangan terkemuka di Asia Tenggara, menyediakan platform perbankan online yang aman dan mudah digunakan bagi pelanggan di Filipina. Dikenal sebagai <strong>Maybank2U</strong>, layanan ini memungkinkan individu dan bisnis untuk mengelola keuangan mereka secara efisien dari kenyamanan rumah atau kantor mereka.</p><p data-block-id=\"deb7cfd0-46be-464a-92c5-b172e70e43a2\">Maybank2U menawarkan berbagai fitur, termasuk transfer dana, pembayaran tagihan, pemantauan akun, dan pembelian pulsa prabayar. Dengan penekanannya pada kemudahan, aksesibilitas, dan keamanan, Maybank2U telah menjadi pilihan populer bagi masyarakat Filipina yang mencari pengalaman perbankan digital yang andal.</p><hr class=\"hr-divider1\"><h2 data-block-id=\"6146dcc6-4245-4158-a034-de0971f8c50b\">Fitur</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"926\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\";max-width:926px;width:926px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:463px;\"><col style=\"width:463px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"402452f7-7a96-45f3-856a-beec3466fb7a\">Kode Channel</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"648b3370-267a-47a5-bafd-0cfb81370827\">MAYBANK_ONLINE_BANKING</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"e924926f-9906-4496-af4a-b319c2a2c8d4\">Mata Uang</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"89cc4585-3036-4f0a-847a-3a0f634c0a27\">PHP</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"6598736d-d850-48ae-b29e-ba649fb13157\">Jumlah Minimum</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"f5c1c704-b8ae-4d25-8fd5-2694332b973d\">1.00</p></